    </step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality Gates (FULL rigor)">
      Run `code-review` + `adr-check` against changed files. Verify ADR-010 / ADR-013 / ADR-029 compliance. Both gates MUST pass.
    </step>
    <step order="10" name="Document + Complete">
      Update task POML status complete. TASK-INDEX 006 ✅. Reset `current-task.md`. Report.
    </step>
  </steps>

